package hkdf // import "crypto/hkdf"

Package hkdf implements the HMAC-based Extract-and-Expand Key Derivation
Function (HKDF) as defined in RFC 5869.

HKDF is a cryptographic key derivation function (KDF) with the goal of expanding
limited input keying material into one or more cryptographically strong secret
keys.

